Header.title: Hi, I'm Deepesh
Header.paragraph: I'm a Full Stack Data Scientist, Machine Learning Engineer & Android Developer.

About.paragraph1: I'am Deepesh - A Full Stack Data Scientist from Mumbai,India. From Analyzing Mountains of Data for Business Intelligence to Making world class AI systems,I like to follow a Data-Centric approach for every problem and aspire to write Clean-Code.
About.paragraph2: One of my superpowers is 'curiosity',I enjoy programming and am highly curious about science, engineering and love studying their impact on our human society.
